title: GET_ENTITY_ROUTING_BUCKET
content:
0xED4B0486// GetEntityRoutingBucket
int GET_ENTITY_ROUTING_BUCKET(Entity entity);Parameters:entity: The entity to get the routing bucket for.Returns: The routing bucket ID.Gets the routing bucket for the specified entity.Routing buckets are also known as 'dimensions' or 'virtual worlds' in past echoes, however they are population-aware.
codeBlocks:
local entity = PlayerPedId()
-- Example usage for GET_ENTITY_ROUTING_BUCKET
GetEntityRoutingBucket(entity)
